"COMPAS is a publicly available rapid binary population synthesis code ... that is designed so that evolution prescriptions and model parameters are easily adjustable. COMPAS draws properties for a binary star system ... and evolves it from zero-age main sequence to the end of its life as two compact remnants."
"Simulations in this paper made use of the COMPAS rapid binary population synthesis code (version X.X.X), which is freely available at http://github.com/TeamCOMPAS/COMPAS."
